   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ECHO HUB Athens: Prepare Refugees for Integration</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In September 2019 we opened our second ECHO HUB, this time in Athens. Given the constant flux of refugees and countless relocations from the islands to the mainland, we recognised the importance of expanding our services and operations to Athens.  Not only does it allow refugees to continue their studies despite relocation, but it also offers a sense of community and support during times of distress and uncertainty.</narrative>
  </description>
